      • onTopicSubmitted

        void onTopicSubmitted(Topic topic,
                      java.lang.String key,
                      java.lang.String value,
                      int version)
        Called when Data successfully submitted. Triggered as a success response as a result of the following method being previously called by this user: Topic.submitData(String key, String value).
        Parameters:
        topic - topic object returning the message.
        key - a unique identifier which is associated with a value.
        value - the single value that is associated to the specified key.
        version - the version of the change - it should be incremented by one for any change that is made to this key-value pair.

      • onTopicDeletedRemotely

        void onTopicDeletedRemotely(Topic topic)
        Called as a result of the topic expiring, or being deleted by another user that is connected to the topic. Triggered as a success response as a result of the following method being previously called by any user: Topic.disconnect(boolean delete) passing true for the delete argument.
        Parameters:
        topic - topic object returning the message

      • onTopicUpdated

        void onTopicUpdated(Topic topic,
                    java.lang.String key,
                    java.lang.String value,
                    int version,
                    boolean deleted)
        Called when the topic is updated, by one of the users connected to the topic calling submitData on the Topic object. Triggered as a success response as a result of the following method being previously called by any user: Topic.submitData(String key, String value).
        Parameters:
        topic - topic object returning the message
        key - a unique identifier which is associated with a value
        value - a value that is retrieved via the use of the unique key.
        version - the version of the change - it should be incremented by one for any change that is made to this key-value pair.
        deleted - whether or not the data has been deleted.

      • onMessageReceived

        void onMessageReceived(Topic topic,
                       java.lang.String message)
        Called as a result of message successfully received. Triggered as a success response as a result of the following method(s) being previously called by any user: Topic.sendAedMessage(String).
        Parameters:
        topic - topic object returning the message
        message - message that was received.
